WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Do you want subtitles for any video?
-=[ ai.OpenSubtitles.com ]=-

2
00:02:30.317 --> 00:02:32.235
There you are.

3
00:02:41.870 --> 00:02:44.873
The sea snake is going to die.
isnthe?

4
00:02:47.668 --> 00:02:50.754
- Luke...
- I can't be lord of the tides.

5
00:02:50.837 --> 00:02:53.423
Grandsire was the greatest sailor
who ever lived.

6
00:02:53.507 --> 00:02:56.385
I get greensick before the ship
even leaves the harbor.

7
00:02:57.094 --> 00:02:58.387
I'll just ruin everything.

8
00:03:00.055 --> 00:03:01.682
I don't want driftmark.

9
00:03:02.474 --> 00:03:04.059
It should've passed on to servaemond.

10
00:03:04.142 --> 00:03:07.312
We don't choose our destiny. Luke.
It chooses us.

11
00:03:07.396 --> 00:03:10.399
Grandsire let you choose
whether you'd be his heir.

12
00:03:11.358 --> 00:03:12.567
You told us so.

13
00:03:17.114 --> 00:03:20.033
And do you want
to know the truth of it?

14
00:03:22.786 --> 00:03:24.079
I was frightened.

15
00:03:25.831 --> 00:03:29.209
I was four-and-ten.

16
00:03:29.292 --> 00:03:30.377
Same as you are now.

17
00:03:31.837 --> 00:03:35.716
I wasn't ready
to be queen of the seven kingdoms.

18
00:03:36.049 --> 00:03:39.261
But it was my duty.

19
00:03:39.344 --> 00:03:41.888
And. in time. I came to understand

20
00:03:41.972 --> 00:03:44.266
I had to earn my inheritance.

21
00:03:46.059 --> 00:03:47.644
I'm not like you.

22
00:03:47.728 --> 00:03:50.063
- In what way. sweet boy?
- I'm not so...

23
00:03:52.816 --> 00:03:53.817
Perfect.

24
00:04:03.827 --> 00:04:05.454
I am anything but.

25
00:04:07.122 --> 00:04:11.042
My father looked after me
and helped to prepare me for my duties.

26
00:04:11.126 --> 00:04:14.254
Your mother will do the same for you.

27
00:04:15.338 --> 00:04:16.673
Good morrow. Princess.

28
00:04:16.757 --> 00:04:17.924
Good morrow. ser lorent.

29
00:04:19.718 --> 00:04:22.262
Princess rhaenys
has just arrived on dragonback.

30
00:04:22.345 --> 00:04:25.056
She urgently requests an audience
with you and prince daemon.

31
00:04:43.325 --> 00:04:45.577
The Princess rhaenys Targaryen.

32
00:04:45.660 --> 00:04:46.745
Thank you. ser lorent.

33
00:04:51.124 --> 00:04:52.918
Princess rhaenys.

34
00:04:53.001 --> 00:04:55.712
might we hope for news
of lord corlys's recovery?

35
00:04:55.796 --> 00:04:57.005
Viserys is dead.

36
00:05:03.512 --> 00:05:06.181
I grieve this loss
with you. rhaenyra.

37
00:05:06.264 --> 00:05:09.142
My cousin. your father...

38
00:05:10.852 --> 00:05:12.312
Possessed a kind heart.

39
00:05:23.615 --> 00:05:24.866
There is more.

40
00:05:26.785 --> 00:05:28.870
Aegon has been crowned as his successor.

41
00:05:36.253 --> 00:05:37.629
They crowned him?

42
00:05:39.714 --> 00:05:42.050
How did viserys die?

43
00:05:42.133 --> 00:05:43.260
I could not say.

44
00:05:44.511 --> 00:05:46.555
- How long ago?
- A day past. perhaps two.

45
00:05:46.638 --> 00:05:49.534
I was made a prisoner in my quarters
while the queen made her preparations.

46
00:05:49.558 --> 00:05:50.809
Viserys has been slain.

47
00:05:52.686 --> 00:05:56.773
Alicent demanded you declare for aegon.

48
00:05:58.608 --> 00:05:59.818
She did.

49
00:06:02.445 --> 00:06:04.698
- I refused her.
- And yet you are alive.

50
00:06:08.201 --> 00:06:10.579
The high septon crowned aegon...

51
00:06:10.662 --> 00:06:11.848
In the dragonpit.

52
00:06:11.872 --> 00:06:14.958
I witnessed it myself
just before I fled on meleys.

53
00:06:15.041 --> 00:06:18.295
They crowned him before the masses.

54
00:06:18.378 --> 00:06:20.773
So that the masses
would see him as their rightful king.

55
00:06:20.797 --> 00:06:24.050
That whore of a queen murdered
my brother and stole his throne.

56
00:06:24.134 --> 00:06:25.774
And you could have
burned them all for it.

57
00:06:26.720 --> 00:06:29.931
A war is like to be fought
over this treachery. to be sure.

58
00:06:31.141 --> 00:06:32.141
Hmm.

59
00:06:33.894 --> 00:06:36.855
But that war is not mine to begin.

60
00:06:37.522 --> 00:06:38.857
I only rushed this warning to you

61
00:06:38.940 --> 00:06:41.902
out of loyalty to my husband
and to my house.

62
00:06:43.612 --> 00:06:45.655
The Greens are coming for you. rhaenyra.

63
00:06:46.907 --> 00:06:48.116
And for your children.

64
00:06:50.076 --> 00:06:52.037
You should leave dragonstone at once.

65
00:07:12.599 --> 00:07:13.642
The babe is coming.

66
00:07:21.816 --> 00:07:23.610
Her term is far from complete.

67
00:07:23.693 --> 00:07:25.379
This should not be happening.

68
00:07:25.403 --> 00:07:27.739
It is fucking happening.

69
00:07:29.324 --> 00:07:31.868
Keep your head about you.
Princess. Come.

70
00:07:33.036 --> 00:07:35.622
We've done this
five times before.

71
00:07:35.705 --> 00:07:38.124
Keep your spirit.
and the sixth will be no different.

72
00:07:38.208 --> 00:07:40.627
Get off. get off.
get off. get off!

73
00:07:40.710 --> 00:07:43.421
Ow. ow. ow.

74
00:07:46.841 --> 00:07:48.694
I want patrols along
the island's perimeter.

75
00:07:48.718 --> 00:07:51.096
looking for any small ships
that might set ashore.

76
00:07:52.263 --> 00:07:55.058
If the Greens attack now.
it will be by stealth...

77
00:07:55.141 --> 00:07:56.577
Not directly.

78
00:07:56.601 --> 00:07:58.481
We don't have enough men
to surround the island.

79
00:07:58.520 --> 00:08:01.106
but we can make ourselves
appear stronger than they are.

80
00:08:04.693 --> 00:08:06.987
Conscript the dragonkeepers.
They're capable fighters.

81
00:08:07.070 --> 00:08:09.489
- Waste no time.
- It will be done. my prince.

82
00:08:21.584 --> 00:08:25.046
- What was that?
- I'm sorry.

83
00:08:25.714 --> 00:08:27.674
You might go easier

84
00:08:27.757 --> 00:08:29.426
on him. my prince.

85
00:08:29.509 --> 00:08:31.845
so he can learn what
you're trying to teach.

86
00:08:31.928 --> 00:08:34.472
Your lady mother
needs to see you!

87
00:08:36.349 --> 00:08:38.143
Both of you.

88
00:08:39.352 --> 00:08:40.895
Mother?

89
00:08:43.940 --> 00:08:44.941
Fuck.

90
00:08:47.819 --> 00:08:48.820
Princess.

91
00:08:59.289 --> 00:09:02.709
Your grandsire. king viserys.
has passed.

92
00:09:02.792 --> 00:09:04.169
Viserys?

93
00:09:04.252 --> 00:09:07.130
The Greens have
repudiated the succession

94
00:09:07.213 --> 00:09:08.923
and claimed the iron throne.

95
00:09:13.053 --> 00:09:14.763
Aegon has been crowned king.

96
00:09:16.264 --> 00:09:18.975
- What is to be done about it?
- Nothing yet.

97
00:09:19.059 --> 00:09:21.728
- And where is daemon?
- I don't know.

98
00:09:21.811 --> 00:09:23.354
Gone to madness.

99
00:09:25.482 --> 00:09:26.733
Gone to plot his war.

100
00:09:28.234 --> 00:09:30.862
- Leave daemon with me.
- Jace.

101
00:09:31.738 --> 00:09:32.781
Jacaerys.

102
00:09:38.495 --> 00:09:42.123
Whatever claim remains to me.
you are now its heir.

103
00:09:42.624 --> 00:09:45.126
Naught is to be done but by my command.

104
00:10:00.600 --> 00:10:01.744
A raven flew in this morning.

105
00:10:01.768 --> 00:10:05.021
The sea snake's fever has broken.
and he has left evenfall.

106
00:10:05.105 --> 00:10:08.566
- Where is he sailing?
- That much is unclear. my prince.

107
00:10:08.650 --> 00:10:10.443
We'll send ravens to our nearest allies.

108
00:10:10.527 --> 00:10:13.029
lords darklyn. massey...

109
00:10:13.822 --> 00:10:15.824
- And bar emmon.
- Daemon!

110
00:10:16.991 --> 00:10:19.410
Do you want to speak
to the maester. my prince?

111
00:10:28.002 --> 00:10:29.480
I'll fly
to the riverlands myself

112
00:10:29.504 --> 00:10:30.839
and affirm lord Tully's support.

113
00:10:30.922 --> 00:10:31.965
You will do no such thing.

114
00:10:35.260 --> 00:10:38.304
My mother has decreed no action be taken
while she's Abed.

115
00:10:44.644 --> 00:10:46.938
It's good you're here. young prince.

116
00:10:48.106 --> 00:10:50.191
You're needed to patrol
the skies on vermax.

117
00:10:50.275 --> 00:10:51.276
Did you hear what I said?

118
00:10:55.864 --> 00:10:57.282
The ravens. lord bartimos.

119
00:10:59.617 --> 00:11:00.785
I shall see it done.

120
00:11:00.869 --> 00:11:02.370
Summon ser steffon.

121
00:11:02.453 --> 00:11:05.081
Our kingsguard are needed
on the dragonmont.

122
00:11:05.707 --> 00:11:08.334
Come with me. I'll show you
the true meaning of loyalty.

123
00:11:16.342 --> 00:11:18.928
You swore an oath
as knights of the kingsguard.

124
00:11:19.012 --> 00:11:21.181
As do all who wear
the white cloak. my prince.

125
00:11:23.057 --> 00:11:24.267
To whom?

126
00:11:25.476 --> 00:11:29.314
I swore first to king jaehaerys.
my prince.

127
00:11:29.397 --> 00:11:30.607
And then to his grace.

128
00:11:30.690 --> 00:11:32.901
king viserys. when he succeeded him.

129
00:11:32.984 --> 00:11:35.111
Do you acknowledge
the true line of succession?

130
00:11:35.945 --> 00:11:37.739
- Yes.
- Yes. my prince.

131
00:11:44.370 --> 00:11:46.414
Do you recall

132
00:11:46.497 --> 00:11:49.042
who king viserys named
as his heir before his death?

133
00:11:52.587 --> 00:11:53.588
Princess rhaenyra.

134
00:11:56.466 --> 00:11:57.466
Hmm.

135
00:11:58.426 --> 00:12:00.470
I'm grateful for
your long service to the crown

136
00:12:03.139 --> 00:12:05.058
so I'm presenting you with a choice.

137
00:12:28.414 --> 00:12:31.000
Swear anew your oath
to rhaenyra as your queen...

138
00:12:32.460 --> 00:12:35.838
To prince jacaerys as the heir
to the iron throne.

139
00:12:40.843 --> 00:12:41.843
Or...

140
00:12:41.886 --> 00:12:44.264
If you support the usurper.
speak it now...

141
00:12:46.140 --> 00:12:48.700
And you will have
a clean and honorable death.

142
00:12:49.477 --> 00:12:51.354
But if you choose treachery.

143
00:12:51.896 --> 00:12:55.275
if you swear fealty now
only to later turn your cloaks...

144
00:12:58.152 --> 00:13:02.031
Know that you will die... screaming.

145
00:13:08.288 --> 00:13:09.956
Princess. let us help you.

146
00:13:12.709 --> 00:13:14.627
No.

147
00:13:17.005 --> 00:13:19.757
- Get out!
- Princess. please.

148
00:13:19.841 --> 00:13:21.652
- Get out.
- You should not do this alone. Princess.

149
00:13:21.676 --> 00:13:22.802
Let us help you.

150
00:13:36.441 --> 00:13:37.775
Ah!

151
00:13:43.865 --> 00:13:44.865
Ah!

152
00:16:47.965 --> 00:16:49.445
I mean no harm. brothers.

153
00:17:13.074 --> 00:17:14.867
I swear to ward the queen...

154
00:17:17.745 --> 00:17:18.788
With all my strength...

155
00:17:21.207 --> 00:17:23.334
And give my blood for hers.

156
00:17:28.381 --> 00:17:29.840
I shall take no wife...

157
00:17:32.009 --> 00:17:33.427
Hold no lands...

158
00:17:34.845 --> 00:17:37.139
Father no children.

159
00:17:37.515 --> 00:17:39.809
I shall guard her secrets...

160
00:17:40.268 --> 00:17:42.061
Obey her commands...

161
00:17:43.145 --> 00:17:46.232
Ride at her side. and defend her name
and honor.

162
00:18:13.467 --> 00:18:14.552
My queen.

163
00:19:56.737 --> 00:19:58.572
Queen rhaenyra Targaryen.

164
00:19:58.656 --> 00:20:00.616
first of her name.

165
00:20:00.700 --> 00:20:03.160
queen of the andals and the rhoynar
and the first men.

166
00:20:04.787 --> 00:20:07.581
Lady of the seven kingdoms
and protector of the realm.

167
00:20:12.002 --> 00:20:13.003
Your grace.

168
00:20:22.096 --> 00:20:23.514
Wine. my queen.

169
00:20:26.851 --> 00:20:27.851
Thank you. rhaena.

170
00:20:29.228 --> 00:20:30.271
Come.

171
00:20:54.837 --> 00:20:56.815
- What is our standing?
- We have 30 knights.

172
00:20:56.839 --> 00:20:59.383
a hundred crossbowmen.
and 300 men-at-arms.

173
00:20:59.467 --> 00:21:01.343
Dragonstone is relatively
easy to defend.

174
00:21:01.427 --> 00:21:02.747
but as an instrument of conquest.

175
00:21:02.803 --> 00:21:05.055
our army leaves a lot to be desired.

176
00:21:05.139 --> 00:21:07.308
We have sent word to my loyal men
in the city watch.

177
00:21:07.391 --> 00:21:09.911
I'll have some support there.
but I cannot speak to the numbers.

178
00:21:09.977 --> 00:21:13.481
We already have declarations
from celtigar and staunton.

179
00:21:13.564 --> 00:21:15.608
massey. darklyn. bar emmon.

180
00:21:18.778 --> 00:21:20.863
My lady mother was an arryn.

181
00:21:20.946 --> 00:21:23.365
The vale will not turn cloak
against their own kin.

182
00:21:23.449 --> 00:21:26.827
Riverrun was always a close friend
to your father. your grace.

183
00:21:26.911 --> 00:21:28.454
With prince daemon's acquiescence.

184
00:21:28.537 --> 00:21:31.040
I've already sent ravens to lord grover.

185
00:21:34.877 --> 00:21:37.254
Lord grover is fickle and easily swayed.

186
00:21:37.338 --> 00:21:39.698
He will need to be convinced
of the strength of our position

187
00:21:39.757 --> 00:21:42.468
and that we will support him
should it come to war.

188
00:21:42.551 --> 00:21:44.595
I'm going to treat with him myself.

189
00:21:44.678 --> 00:21:46.388
What of storm's end
and winterfell?

190
00:21:46.472 --> 00:21:49.099
There has never
lived a stark who forgot an oath.

191
00:21:49.183 --> 00:21:51.894
And with house stark.
the north will follow.

192
00:21:51.977 --> 00:21:55.606
Lord borros Baratheon will need
to be reminded of his father's promises.

193
00:22:08.702 --> 00:22:10.204
What news from driftmark?

194
00:22:13.499 --> 00:22:15.376
Lord corlys sails for dragonstone.

195
00:22:15.459 --> 00:22:17.086
To declare for his queen.

196
00:22:19.088 --> 00:22:22.049
The velaryon fleet
is in my husband's yoke.

197
00:22:22.132 --> 00:22:24.009
He decides where they sail.

198
00:22:24.093 --> 00:22:27.388
We shall pray for both you
and your husband's support.

199
00:22:27.471 --> 00:22:30.558
Just as we prayed nightly for
the sea snake's return to good health.

200
00:22:32.184 --> 00:22:33.912
There's no port on the narrow sea
would dare to make

201
00:22:33.936 --> 00:22:35.896
an enemy of the velaryon fleet.

202
00:22:37.982 --> 00:22:38.982
And our enemies?

203
00:22:39.024 --> 00:22:40.624
We have no friends among the lannisters.

204
00:22:41.360 --> 00:22:44.363
Tyland has served the hand
too long to turn against him.

205
00:22:44.446 --> 00:22:46.615
And Otto hightower
needs the Lannister fleet.

206
00:22:46.699 --> 00:22:48.260
Without the lannisters.
we are not like to find

207
00:22:48.284 --> 00:22:50.644
- any allies west of the golden tooth.
- No.

208
00:22:53.789 --> 00:22:55.708
The riverlands are essential.
your grace.

209
00:22:57.376 --> 00:23:00.754
Pray forgive my bluntness. your grace.
but talk of men is moot.

210
00:23:01.422 --> 00:23:05.050
Your cause owns a power
that has not been seen in this world

211
00:23:05.134 --> 00:23:07.636
since the days of old valyria.

212
00:23:07.720 --> 00:23:08.846
Dragons.

213
00:23:12.099 --> 00:23:13.517
The Greens have dragons as well.

214
00:23:13.601 --> 00:23:15.603
They have three adults. by my count.

215
00:23:15.686 --> 00:23:18.522
We have syrax. caraxes. and meleys.

216
00:23:18.606 --> 00:23:21.525
Your sons have
vermax. arrax. and tyraxes.

217
00:23:21.609 --> 00:23:23.527
Baela has moondancer.

218
00:23:23.611 --> 00:23:25.371
Daemon. none of our dragons
have been to war.

219
00:23:25.404 --> 00:23:27.907
There are also unclaimed dragons.

220
00:23:27.990 --> 00:23:29.617
Seasmoke still resides on driftmark.

221
00:23:29.700 --> 00:23:32.578
Vermithor and silvenning
dwell on the dragonmont.

222
00:23:32.661 --> 00:23:33.829
still riderless.

223
00:23:34.830 --> 00:23:37.249
Then there are the three wild dragons.
all of whom nest here.

224
00:23:37.333 --> 00:23:38.602
And who is to ride them?

225
00:23:38.626 --> 00:23:41.003
Dragonstone has 13 to their 4.

226
00:23:42.046 --> 00:23:45.215
I also have a score of eggs
incubating in the dragonmont.

227
00:23:45.299 --> 00:23:48.761
Now... we need a place to gather.

228
00:23:48.844 --> 00:23:52.431
a toehold large enough
to house a sizable host.

229
00:23:52.514 --> 00:23:53.515
Here. at harrenhal.

230
00:23:53.599 --> 00:23:54.516
We cut off the west.

231
00:23:54.600 --> 00:23:56.200
surround king's landing
with the dragons.

232
00:23:56.226 --> 00:23:58.079
And we could have every green head
mounted on spikes

233
00:23:58.103 --> 00:23:59.980
before the fucking moon turns.

234
00:24:00.064 --> 00:24:01.649
Your grace...

235
00:24:01.732 --> 00:24:03.525
A ship has been sighted offshore.

236
00:24:03.609 --> 00:24:06.153
alone galleon. flying a banner
of a three-headed green dragon.

237
00:24:06.236 --> 00:24:08.556
Alert the watchtowers. Sight the skies.

238
00:24:46.110 --> 00:24:49.071
I come at the behest
of the dowager queen alicent.

239
00:24:49.154 --> 00:24:51.323
mother of king aegon.
second of his name.

240
00:24:51.407 --> 00:24:54.201
lord and protector
of the seven kingdoms.

241
00:24:55.035 --> 00:24:58.580
I've been directed to deliver
her message only to Princess rhaenyra.

242
00:25:00.374 --> 00:25:02.292
Where is the Princess?

243
00:25:56.722 --> 00:25:58.766
Princess rhaenyra.

244
00:25:59.725 --> 00:26:01.018
I'm queen rhaenyra now.

245
00:26:02.603 --> 00:26:04.855
And you all are traitors to the realm.

246
00:26:05.355 --> 00:26:09.151
King aegon Targaryen.
second of his name...

247
00:26:10.861 --> 00:26:14.323
In his wisdom and desire for peace.

248
00:26:14.406 --> 00:26:15.908
is offering terms.

249
00:26:18.285 --> 00:26:19.995
Acknowledge aegon as king

250
00:26:20.079 --> 00:26:22.915
and swear obeisance
before the iron throne.

251
00:26:22.998 --> 00:26:26.710
In exchange. his grace will confirm
your possession of dragonstone.

252
00:26:27.544 --> 00:26:31.173
It will pass to your trueborn son.
jacaerys. upon your death.

253
00:26:31.256 --> 00:26:34.593
Lucerys will be confirmed
as the legitimate heir to driftmark

254
00:26:34.676 --> 00:26:37.554
and all the lands and holdings
of house velaryon.

255
00:26:37.638 --> 00:26:39.431
Your sons by prince daemon

256
00:26:39.515 --> 00:26:42.434
will also be given places
of high honor at court.

257
00:26:42.976 --> 00:26:44.978
aegon the younger as the king's squire.

258
00:26:45.062 --> 00:26:47.106
viserys as his cupbearer.

259
00:26:47.189 --> 00:26:49.149
Finally. the king. in his good grace.

260
00:26:49.233 --> 00:26:53.695
will pardon any knight or lord
who conspired against his ascent.

261
00:26:54.404 --> 00:26:57.157
I would rather feed my sons
to the dragons

262
00:26:57.241 --> 00:27:00.369
than have them carry shields and cups

263
00:27:00.452 --> 00:27:04.123
for your drunken.
usurper cunt of a king.

264
00:27:04.581 --> 00:27:07.793
Aegon Targaryen sits the iron throne.

265
00:27:09.044 --> 00:27:10.838
He wears the conqueror's crown.

266
00:27:10.921 --> 00:27:12.673
wields the conqueror's sword.

267
00:27:12.756 --> 00:27:14.174
has the conqueror's name.

268
00:27:14.633 --> 00:27:17.052
He was anointed by a septon of the faith

269
00:27:17.136 --> 00:27:19.012
before the eyes of thousands.

270
00:27:19.096 --> 00:27:23.016
Every symbol of legitimacy
belongs to him.

271
00:27:25.561 --> 00:27:28.856
And then there is stark.
Tully. Baratheon.

272
00:27:28.939 --> 00:27:32.985
Houses that have also received.
and are at present.

273
00:27:33.068 --> 00:27:36.280
considering generous terms
from their king.

274
00:27:38.073 --> 00:27:40.951
Stark. Tully. and Baratheon
all swore to me

275
00:27:42.202 --> 00:27:44.872
when king viserys named me his heir.

276
00:27:45.581 --> 00:27:49.418
Stale oaths will not put you
on the iron throne. Princess.

277
00:27:50.085 --> 00:27:54.089
The succession changed the day
your father sired a son.

278
00:27:54.590 --> 00:27:58.510
I only regret that you and he
were the last to see the truth of it.

279
00:27:59.511 --> 00:28:01.805
You are no more hand than aegon is king.

280
00:28:01.889 --> 00:28:03.515
Fucking traitor.

281
00:28:15.277 --> 00:28:16.904
Grand maester.

282
00:28:22.201 --> 00:28:23.368
What the fuck is this?

283
00:28:38.926 --> 00:28:42.512
Queen alicent has not forgotten
the love you once had for each other.

284
00:28:44.056 --> 00:28:49.561
No blood need be spilled.
The realm can carry on in peace.

285
00:28:53.065 --> 00:28:55.359
Queen alicent eagerly
awaits your answer.

286
00:28:55.442 --> 00:28:57.723
She can have her answer now.
stuffed in her father's mouth

287
00:28:57.778 --> 00:28:58.987
along with his withered cock.

288
00:28:59.071 --> 00:29:00.781
Let's end this mummer's farce.

289
00:29:02.532 --> 00:29:05.869
Ser erryk. bring me lord hightower
so I may take the pleasure myself.

290
00:29:23.637 --> 00:29:25.806
King's landing will have
my answer on the morrow.

291
00:29:48.287 --> 00:29:51.248
It's no easy thing
for a man to be a dragonslayer.

292
00:29:52.332 --> 00:29:54.751
But dragons can kill dragons. And have.

293
00:29:56.295 --> 00:29:59.464
The simple truth is this.
we have more dragons than aegon.

294
00:29:59.715 --> 00:30:02.134
Viserys spoke often
of the valyrian histories.

295
00:30:02.217 --> 00:30:03.218
I know them well.

296
00:30:04.469 --> 00:30:06.179
When dragons flew to war...

297
00:30:07.514 --> 00:30:08.682
Everything burned.

298
00:30:11.101 --> 00:30:14.187
I do not wish to rule
over a kingdom of ash and bone.

299
00:30:14.271 --> 00:30:16.690
Are you considering
the hightowers' terms. your grace?

300
00:30:17.607 --> 00:30:21.320
As queen. what is my true duty
to the realm. lord bartimos?

301
00:30:21.820 --> 00:30:23.363
Ensuring peace and unity?

302
00:30:23.447 --> 00:30:26.325
Or that I sit the iron throne.
no matter the cost?

303
00:30:26.408 --> 00:30:28.702
- That's your father talking.
- My father's dead.

304
00:30:30.787 --> 00:30:32.998
And he chose me as his successor...

305
00:30:35.375 --> 00:30:37.919
To defend the realm.
not cast it headlong into war.

306
00:30:38.003 --> 00:30:39.379
Well. the enemy have declared war.

307
00:30:40.255 --> 00:30:41.798
What are you gonna do about it?

308
00:30:45.385 --> 00:30:46.595
Clear the room.

309
00:31:17.084 --> 00:31:18.668
Does the promise of war excite you?

310
00:31:18.752 --> 00:31:20.545
You cannot bend the knee
to the hightowers.

311
00:31:20.629 --> 00:31:22.172
They stole your birthright.

312
00:31:22.255 --> 00:31:23.941
If you could
take the iron throne

313
00:31:23.965 --> 00:31:26.051
without putting Otto hightower's
head on a spike.

314
00:31:26.134 --> 00:31:27.653
- would you?
- Are you not angry?

315
00:31:27.677 --> 00:31:30.073
- I should declare war because I'm angry?
- No.

316
00:31:30.097 --> 00:31:32.140
Because it's your duty
as queen to crush rebellion.

317
00:31:32.224 --> 00:31:35.936
You know my oath
reaches beyond our personal ambitions.

318
00:31:39.231 --> 00:31:40.732
A song of ice and fire.

319
00:31:43.860 --> 00:31:44.861
What?

320
00:31:46.363 --> 00:31:48.132
The coming war against
the darkness in the north.

321
00:31:48.156 --> 00:31:49.241
The conqueror's dream.

322
00:31:50.283 --> 00:31:52.244
Viserys shared it with me
when he named me heir.

323
00:31:57.290 --> 00:32:01.294
My brother... was a slave to his
omens and portents.

324
00:32:02.546 --> 00:32:05.799
Anything to make his feckless reign
appear to have purpose.

325
00:32:09.803 --> 00:32:11.346
Dreams didn't make us kings.

326
00:32:12.848 --> 00:32:13.932
Dragons did.

327
00:32:32.409 --> 00:32:33.743
He never told you...

328
00:32:37.789 --> 00:32:38.999
Did he?

329
00:33:16.286 --> 00:33:20.123
I've had men whipped for falling asleep
on their watch.

330
00:33:26.671 --> 00:33:27.756
You are no man.

331
00:33:33.011 --> 00:33:34.221
You abandoned me...

332
00:33:36.598 --> 00:33:37.807
When I most needed you.

333
00:33:39.518 --> 00:33:41.311
Both our children stolen from us.

334
00:33:43.188 --> 00:33:44.356
I needed you.

335
00:33:45.065 --> 00:33:46.483
Baela and rhaena needed you.

336
00:33:46.566 --> 00:33:49.653
and you abandoned us
for more adventure at sea.

337
00:33:49.736 --> 00:33:51.780
As has always been your way.

338
00:33:53.490 --> 00:33:55.575
I had no other place to turn.

339
00:33:57.369 --> 00:34:00.247
- I lost everything.
- We lost. corlys.

340
00:34:16.721 --> 00:34:18.265
I understand we have a new king.

341
00:34:19.099 --> 00:34:21.893
The stranger casts a long shadow
over this family.

342
00:34:28.858 --> 00:34:30.443
Your brother is also dead.

343
00:34:35.699 --> 00:34:38.660
In his haste to Bury you
and claim your seat.

344
00:34:38.743 --> 00:34:40.245
he stood before the king

345
00:34:40.328 --> 00:34:43.206
and denounced
laenor's sons as illegitimate.

346
00:34:48.295 --> 00:34:49.754
Daemon took his head for it.

347
00:34:55.468 --> 00:34:59.180
Heedless ambition has always been
a velaryon weakness.

348
00:35:04.311 --> 00:35:05.937
You were right. rhaenys.

349
00:35:08.064 --> 00:35:11.318
I reached too far. And for nothing.

350
00:35:13.945 --> 00:35:18.533
Our pursuit of the iron throne...
Is at an end.

351
00:35:23.246 --> 00:35:25.665
We shall declare for no one.

352
00:35:27.667 --> 00:35:29.294
We will retire to high tide

353
00:35:29.919 --> 00:35:31.046
to be content...

354
00:35:32.088 --> 00:35:34.466
With our grandchildren and...

355
00:35:34.549 --> 00:35:37.260
Jace. Luke. and joff
are claimants to the throne.

356
00:35:39.429 --> 00:35:41.973
Those boys'll not be safe
so long as aegon is king.

357
00:35:44.809 --> 00:35:48.605
Rhaenyra was complicit
in our son's death.

358
00:35:50.440 --> 00:35:53.068
That girl destroys
everything she touches.

359
00:35:53.151 --> 00:35:55.111
That "girl"...

360
00:35:55.195 --> 00:35:57.197
Is holding the realm together
at present.

361
00:35:58.448 --> 00:36:00.241
Every man standing
'round the painted table

362
00:36:00.325 --> 00:36:02.160
urges her to plunge the realm into war.

363
00:36:04.871 --> 00:36:08.083
Rhaenyra's the only
one who's demonstrated restraint.

364
00:36:08.166 --> 00:36:10.335
The purpose of war
is to fill graveyards.

365
00:36:10.418 --> 00:36:11.503
my dear lord staunton.

366
00:36:11.586 --> 00:36:14.756
The trick is to put more of their men
in the ground than your own.

367
00:36:14.839 --> 00:36:16.442
Easy words
for a lord who commands

368
00:36:16.466 --> 00:36:18.069
- from the safety of his castle.
- Doesn't make it any less true.

369
00:36:18.093 --> 00:36:19.453
The lord of the tides!

370
00:36:20.387 --> 00:36:21.805
Lord corlys velaryon...

371
00:36:23.264 --> 00:36:26.434
And his wife.
the Princess rhaenys Targaryen.

372
00:36:38.196 --> 00:36:39.781
My lords.

373
00:36:39.864 --> 00:36:41.491
Lord corlys.

374
00:36:42.325 --> 00:36:45.036
It brings much relief to see you hale
and healthy again.

375
00:36:47.455 --> 00:36:50.291
I'm very sorry about your father.
Princess.

376
00:36:50.834 --> 00:36:52.836
He was a good man.

377
00:37:04.097 --> 00:37:05.306
Where is daemon?

378
00:37:06.433 --> 00:37:09.436
There were other concerns which
demanded the prince's attention.

379
00:37:10.979 --> 00:37:11.979
Mmm.

380
00:37:20.780 --> 00:37:22.198
Your declared allies?

381
00:37:23.742 --> 00:37:26.745
- Yes.
- Too few to win a war for the throne.

382
00:37:28.997 --> 00:37:31.666
Well. we would also
hope to have the support

383
00:37:31.750 --> 00:37:34.753
- of houses arryn. Baratheon. and stark.
- Hope...

384
00:37:35.628 --> 00:37:37.172
Is the fool's ally.

385
00:37:38.798 --> 00:37:42.010
Both arryn and Baratheon
share blood with my house.

386
00:37:42.093 --> 00:37:44.137
But all of them swore oaths to me.

387
00:37:44.220 --> 00:37:46.055
As did house hightower...

388
00:37:46.139 --> 00:37:47.307
If I remember.

389
00:37:47.390 --> 00:37:50.435
As did you. lord corlys.

390
00:38:04.199 --> 00:38:05.617
Your father's realm...

391
00:38:06.743 --> 00:38:09.662
Was one of justice and honor.

392
00:38:10.705 --> 00:38:14.793
Our houses are bound by common blood
and common cause.

393
00:38:16.711 --> 00:38:19.714
This hightower treason cannot stand.

394
00:38:25.345 --> 00:38:28.556
You have the full support
of our fleet and house.

395
00:38:30.517 --> 00:38:31.518
Your grace.

396
00:38:40.568 --> 00:38:42.362
You honor me. lord corlys.

397
00:38:48.535 --> 00:38:50.578
Princess rhaenys.

398
00:38:54.582 --> 00:38:58.253
But. as I said to my bannermen.

399
00:38:58.336 --> 00:39:01.965
I made a promise to my father
to hold the realm strong and united.

400
00:39:03.883 --> 00:39:06.970
If war's first stroke is to fall.
it will not be by my hand.

401
00:39:08.429 --> 00:39:09.806
You do not mean to act?

402
00:39:09.889 --> 00:39:13.393
Taking caution
does not mean standing fast.

403
00:39:13.476 --> 00:39:18.481
I wish to know who my allies are
before I send them to war.

404
00:39:26.197 --> 00:39:27.532
The consequence of my...

405
00:39:28.741 --> 00:39:31.744
Near-demise in the stepstones...

406
00:39:32.996 --> 00:39:34.831
Is that we now control them.

407
00:39:35.498 --> 00:39:38.084
I took care to fully Garrison
the territory this time.

408
00:39:38.167 --> 00:39:40.003
A total blockade of the shipping lanes

409
00:39:40.086 --> 00:39:43.131
will be in place in days.
if not already.

410
00:39:43.214 --> 00:39:45.633
The triarchy have been routed.

411
00:39:45.717 --> 00:39:47.677
The narrow sea is ours.

412
00:39:50.471 --> 00:39:53.266
If we further seal the gullet.

413
00:39:53.349 --> 00:39:56.352
we can cut off
all seaborne travel and trade

414
00:39:56.436 --> 00:39:57.687
to king's landing.

415
00:39:58.688 --> 00:40:01.190
I shall take meleys
and patrol the gullet myself.

416
00:40:06.404 --> 00:40:08.114
When we drain the narrow sea.

417
00:40:09.282 --> 00:40:11.284
we can surround king's landing.

418
00:40:11.367 --> 00:40:13.620
lay siege to the red keep.

419
00:40:13.703 --> 00:40:16.164
and force the Greens' surrender.

420
00:40:16.247 --> 00:40:19.959
If we are to have enough swords
to surround king's landing.

421
00:40:20.043 --> 00:40:23.671
we must first secure the support of
winterfell. the eyrie. and storm's end.

422
00:40:23.755 --> 00:40:25.798
I'll prepare the ravens. your grace.

423
00:40:26.633 --> 00:40:28.233
We should bear those messages.

424
00:40:30.178 --> 00:40:32.263
Dragons can fly faster than ravens

425
00:40:33.222 --> 00:40:34.349
and they're more convincing.

426
00:40:38.394 --> 00:40:39.604
Send us.

427
00:40:41.522 --> 00:40:42.982
The prince is right. your grace.

428
00:40:52.617 --> 00:40:53.660
Very well.

429
00:40:54.661 --> 00:40:56.788
Prince jacaerys will fly north.

430
00:40:57.830 --> 00:41:01.000
First to the eyrie to see my mother's
cousin. the lady jeyne arryn.

431
00:41:01.084 --> 00:41:04.003
and then to winterfell
to treat with lord cregan stark

432
00:41:04.087 --> 00:41:06.005
for the support of the north.

433
00:41:07.131 --> 00:41:09.926
Prince lucerys will fly
south to storm's end

434
00:41:10.009 --> 00:41:12.804
and treat with lord borros Baratheon.

435
00:41:12.887 --> 00:41:17.016
We must remind these lords
of the oaths they swore.

436
00:41:18.643 --> 00:41:21.104
And... the cost of breaking them.

437
00:41:45.753 --> 00:41:50.299
It's been said that as targaryens.
we are closer to gods than to men.

438
00:41:52.844 --> 00:41:55.346
And the iron throne
puts us a touch closer. perhaps.

439
00:41:57.557 --> 00:42:01.185
But. if we are to serve
the seven kingdoms...

440
00:42:02.520 --> 00:42:04.981
We must answer to their gods.

441
00:42:05.523 --> 00:42:10.069
If you take this errand.
you go as messengers... not as warriors.

442
00:42:10.695 --> 00:42:12.864
You must take no part in any fighting.

443
00:42:14.699 --> 00:42:18.036
Swear it to me now
under the eyes of the seven.

444
00:42:23.541 --> 00:42:24.709
I swear it.

445
00:42:29.589 --> 00:42:30.757
I swear it.

446
00:42:31.966 --> 00:42:32.967
Thank you.

447
00:42:36.679 --> 00:42:38.681
Cregan stark is...

448
00:42:39.557 --> 00:42:41.100
Closer to your age than to mine.

449
00:42:41.726 --> 00:42:45.396
I would hope. that as men.
you can find some common interest.

450
00:42:46.606 --> 00:42:47.690
Yes. your grace.

451
00:42:56.365 --> 00:42:58.576
Storm's end is a short flight from here.

452
00:43:00.369 --> 00:43:03.873
You have Baratheon blood
from your grandmother. rhaenys.

453
00:43:03.956 --> 00:43:05.291
And...

454
00:43:05.374 --> 00:43:07.794
Lord borros is an eternally proud man.

455
00:43:08.753 --> 00:43:11.631
He will be honored
to host a prince of the realm...

456
00:43:12.882 --> 00:43:14.217
And his dragon.

457
00:43:23.184 --> 00:43:25.728
I expect you will receive
a very warm welcome.

458
00:43:27.772 --> 00:43:29.524
Yes. mother. Your grace.

459
00:43:39.033 --> 00:43:40.785
Go to it then.

460
00:47:21.964 --> 00:47:23.716
I am prince lucerys velaryon.

461
00:47:24.717 --> 00:47:26.802
I bring a message to lord borros
from the queen.

462
00:47:43.861 --> 00:47:45.488
Prince lucerys velaryon.

463
00:47:52.370 --> 00:47:55.373
Son
of Princess rhaenyra Targaryen.

464
00:47:59.960 --> 00:48:01.379
Lord borros...

465
00:48:03.172 --> 00:48:04.882
I brought you a message
from my mother...

466
00:48:06.300 --> 00:48:07.510
The queen.

467
00:48:08.552 --> 00:48:11.514
Yet earlier this day.
I received an envoy from the king.

468
00:48:13.140 --> 00:48:14.183
Which is it?

469
00:48:14.892 --> 00:48:17.603
King or queen?

470
00:48:17.686 --> 00:48:20.189
The house of the dragon
does not seem to know who rules it.

471
00:48:23.192 --> 00:48:24.985
What's your mother's message?

472
00:48:41.919 --> 00:48:43.629
Where's the bloody maester?

473
00:49:18.456 --> 00:49:21.709
"Remind" me of my father's oath?

474
00:49:23.544 --> 00:49:25.504
King aegon at least came with an offer.

475
00:49:25.588 --> 00:49:28.382
my swords and banners
for a marriage pact.

476
00:49:29.675 --> 00:49:31.635
If I do as your mother bids...

477
00:49:32.970 --> 00:49:35.306
Which one of my daughters
will you wed...

478
00:49:39.185 --> 00:49:42.271
My lord... I am not free to marry.

479
00:49:43.689 --> 00:49:45.024
I'm already betrothed.

480
00:49:47.359 --> 00:49:49.653
So you come with empty hands.

481
00:49:51.864 --> 00:49:54.033
Go home. pup.

482
00:49:54.116 --> 00:49:56.285
And tell your mother
that the lord of storm's end

483
00:49:56.368 --> 00:50:00.956
is not some dog that she can whistle up
at need to set against her foes.

484
00:50:03.125 --> 00:50:06.462
I shall take your answer
to the queen. my lord.

485
00:50:13.219 --> 00:50:14.303
Wait...

486
00:50:16.597 --> 00:50:18.015
My lord strong.

487
00:50:23.062 --> 00:50:27.399
Did you really think
that you could just fly about the realm

488
00:50:27.483 --> 00:50:30.110
trying to steal my brother's throne
at no cost?

489
00:50:31.862 --> 00:50:33.072
I will not fight you.

490
00:50:34.615 --> 00:50:37.493
I came as a messenger. not a warrior.

491
00:50:37.576 --> 00:50:39.203
A fight would be little challenge.

492
00:50:44.375 --> 00:50:46.377
I want you to put out your eye.

493
00:50:49.296 --> 00:50:50.631
As payment for mine.

494
00:50:53.050 --> 00:50:54.134
One will serve.

495
00:50:58.389 --> 00:50:59.598
I would not blind you.

496
00:51:02.935 --> 00:51:05.145
Plan to make
a gift of it to my mother.

497
00:51:11.694 --> 00:51:13.654
Then you are craven
as well as a traitor.

498
00:51:13.737 --> 00:51:15.781
- Not here.
- Give me your eye.

499
00:51:16.365 --> 00:51:17.992
or I will take it. bastard!

500
00:51:18.993 --> 00:51:20.411
Not in my hall!

501
00:51:21.579 --> 00:51:23.372
The boy came as an envoy.

502
00:51:23.455 --> 00:51:25.416
I'll not have bloodshed beneath my roof.

503
00:51:26.083 --> 00:51:28.252
Take prince lucerys back to his dragon.

504
00:51:29.086 --> 00:51:30.087
Now.

505
00:53:31.083 --> 00:53:32.710
{933931 -

